high_descs: Turn left, walk towards the stove and turn left. Go forward to reach the counter on the left.
Pick up the form on the right side of the counter.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right to go to the kitchen sink.
Place the fork in the sink and turn on the water for a few seconds, then turn off the water.
Pick up the fork from the sink.
Turn left and open the second drawer on the right, place the fork in and close it.
anns.task_desc: Wash a fork and place inside kitchen drawer.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the stove then turn left and walk to the counter on your left and turn left when you get to it to face it.
Pick up the fork that's near the corner near you.
Turn around and take two steps then turn right and walk to the sink that's in front of you.
Wash the fork in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Open the drawer on your right closest to the corner in front of you and put the fork in there before closing the drawer again.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean fork in the drawer.

high_descs: Turn to the left and take two steps, then turn to the left and take two steps, then turn t the left and walk to the counter.
Pick up the fork that is near the spoon on the counter.
Turn left and walk two steps, then turn right and walk to the counter.
Put the fork in the sink, turn the water on for three seconds, then turn the water off and pick up the spoon.
Turn to the left and look at the cabinets.
Open the furthest drawer on the right side and put the fork in the drawer.
